WEBVTT

1
00:00:11.707 --> 00:00:14.547
Raziel!

2
00:00:14.627 --> 00:00:18.428
Fin Raziel!
I have to talk to you. please!

3
00:00:22.347 --> 00:00:24.937
Raziel!

4
00:00:29.767 --> 00:00:33.437
She's not here.

5
00:00:36.448 --> 00:00:38.367
- Aah!

6
00:00:38.448 --> 00:00:41.987
Get back! Who are you?

7
00:00:43.117 --> 00:00:45.997
Who are you?

8
00:00:48.417 --> 00:00:51.497
- I'm Willow Ufgood.
- What are you doing here?

9
00:00:51.587 --> 00:00:55.257
I've come to find the great
sorceress. Fin Raziel.

10
00:00:55.337 --> 00:00:57.928
That's me!
I'm Raziel!

11
00:00:59.968 --> 00:01:01.887
This can't be right!

12
00:01:01.968 --> 00:01:05.477
One of Bavmorda's spells
transformed me.

13
00:01:07.767 --> 00:01:10.357
Believe me. it could
have been worse!

14
00:01:10.437 --> 00:01:16.237
Oh. Well. this wand is for you.
It's from Cherlindrea.

15
00:01:16.317 --> 00:01:20.817
Then the prophecy is true.
The princess has been born.

16
00:01:20.908 --> 00:01:22.867
Take me to her.

17
00:01:25.408 --> 00:01:28.167
It is Blora Danan.

18
00:01:28.247 --> 00:01:31.167
Isn't she beautiful?

19
00:01:31.247 --> 00:01:34.207
Isn't she beautiful?

20
00:01:34.297 --> 00:01:37.797
- That's Raziel?
- I don't know. I-

21
00:01:37.877 --> 00:01:40.137
I expected something
more grand. Less. uh-

22
00:01:40.178 --> 00:01:42.137
- Fuzzy.
- Fuzzy!

23
00:01:42.218 --> 00:01:46.017
You must use the wand.
Turn me back into my human form.

24
00:01:46.097 --> 00:01:49.437
- What do I do?
- You mean you're not a sorcerer?

25
00:01:50.647 --> 00:01:53.147
Yes. Sort a.

26
00:01:53.227 --> 00:01:55.727
-I'm a farmer.

27
00:01:55.817 --> 00:01:57.737
But I do know a few tricks.

28
00:01:57.777 --> 00:02:03.327
Tricks? Cherlindrea sent you?
You must learn real magic.

29
00:02:03.448 --> 00:02:07.497
- Horses! Horses!

30
00:02:07.577 --> 00:02:10.077
Quick! Take her!
Hurry! Hurry!

31
00:02:18.877 --> 00:02:21.837
I knew he was a traitor!

32
00:02:24.428 --> 00:02:27.137
- Sorry about this. peck.
- Keep your mouth shut!

33
00:02:28.178 --> 00:02:30.977
Told you we'd find him
without your help.

34
00:02:31.057 --> 00:02:33.017
- Give me that baby.
- No!

35
00:02:36.477 --> 00:02:40.448
- Give her back!
- Leave me alone! Don't touch me!

36
00:02:46.367 --> 00:02:48.247
This is the one
we're looking for.

37
00:02:48.327 --> 00:02:51.707
- We must take it back to Nockmaar.

38
00:02:54.497 --> 00:02:56.417
Lose your skirt?

39
00:03:04.087 --> 00:03:06.047
I've still got what counts.

40
00:03:06.097 --> 00:03:08.428
Not for long.

41
00:03:14.267 --> 00:03:17.817
- Bring him.
- Over here!

42
00:03:35.497 --> 00:03:38.247
We'll never keep up
with those horses.

43
00:03:38.297 --> 00:03:40.257
Then we will
have to track them.

44
00:03:40.297 --> 00:03:41.718
That would take forever.

45
00:03:41.797 --> 00:03:44.547
Besides. even if we find them.
they'll catch us.

46
00:03:44.587 --> 00:03:47.797
stick us in cages. torture us
and finally devour us.

47
00:03:47.887 --> 00:03:49.847
Are you suggesting
we go home?

48
00:03:49.928 --> 00:03:52.847
- Nah. This is more fun!
- All right.

49
00:03:52.937 --> 00:03:54.847
Fine. then.
Come on!

50
00:04:08.658 --> 00:04:12.117
I'm worried about Blora.
She doesn't sound good.

51
00:04:12.158 --> 00:04:14.957
Hurry! Practice
the chant I taught you!

52
00:04:14.997 --> 00:04:20.797
- Tanna... looatha- Oh. I can't
remember the middle part.

53
00:04:20.877 --> 00:04:22.917
Locktwaar!

54
00:04:22.968 --> 00:04:25.968
That's the word
that pleads for change.

55
00:04:26.047 --> 00:04:28.007
Locktwaar.

56
00:04:31.678 --> 00:04:34.847
Blora's cold and hungry.
She knows me.

57
00:04:34.937 --> 00:04:36.847
Please. let me
take care of her.

58
00:04:36.937 --> 00:04:39.057
I don't need help
from a peck.

59
00:04:42.817 --> 00:04:46.857
- What are you staring at?
- Your leg.

60
00:04:46.948 --> 00:04:49.317
I'd like to break it.

61
00:04:49.367 --> 00:04:54.247
You may find that difficult while
I'm up here and you're down there.

62
00:04:57.367 --> 00:04:59.587
I hate that woman.

63
00:05:32.237 --> 00:05:34.327
Hyah!

64
00:05:38.117 --> 00:05:40.917
- I found it. Kael.

65
00:05:42.037 --> 00:05:45.087
That should make
my mother happy.

66
00:05:45.167 --> 00:05:48.178
What are they gonna do to her?

67
00:06:00.727 --> 00:06:03.397
Hither walha...

68
00:06:03.477 --> 00:06:07.027
bairn derubordak...

69
00:06:07.107 --> 00:06:09.027
- bellanockt.

70
00:06:09.107 --> 00:06:11.987
That's magic?
Smells terrible.

71
00:06:12.067 --> 00:06:15.287
- It's the life spark. It forms after-
- Well. it stinks!

72
00:06:15.367 --> 00:06:18.537
- This whole thing stinks!
- Ignore him. Willow.

73
00:06:18.617 --> 00:06:21.627
- He's a fool!
- If only I had a sword!

74
00:06:21.707 --> 00:06:24.797
- If only you'd quit talking about it.

75
00:06:24.877 --> 00:06:28.257
Willow. you must transform me
to my human self.

76
00:06:28.297 --> 00:06:31.127
But. Raziel.
I'm not ready yet.

77
00:06:31.218 --> 00:06:34.428
You'd better be.
Get me down.

78
00:06:38.057 --> 00:06:40.477
Ow!

79
00:06:43.107 --> 00:06:46.107
Why don't you help me get out of here
instead of chattering with that muskrat?

80
00:06:46.187 --> 00:06:48.937
Muskrat!
When I change back...

81
00:06:48.987 --> 00:06:52.948
to my former self.
I will crush this army.

82
00:06:53.027 --> 00:06:55.698
and take Blora Danan
to Tir Asleen...

83
00:06:55.777 --> 00:06:58.368
where she will be safe.

84
00:06:58.448 --> 00:07:00.788
- Ow!

85
00:07:00.828 --> 00:07:02.788
What'd you bite me for?

86
00:07:02.828 --> 00:07:06.168
You need three drops
of your blood to put in the potion.

87
00:07:06.248 --> 00:07:09.547
- Well. you coulda warned me.

88
00:07:09.627 --> 00:07:12.047
For beginners.
there's some pain.

89
00:07:12.127 --> 00:07:17.217
but don't let anything
break your concentration.

90
00:07:22.347 --> 00:07:25.227
Hit her green anbairn
claideblunanockt.

91
00:07:25.307 --> 00:07:29.067
- Hello. everybody! We have arrived!
- You are saved.

92
00:07:29.147 --> 00:07:31.987
- Shh!
- Don't interrupt.

93
00:07:33.408 --> 00:07:36.578
Hit her green anbairn
claideblunanockt.

94
00:07:36.658 --> 00:07:39.487
What are you going
to look like if this works?

95
00:07:39.578 --> 00:07:42.078
- Don't interrupt.
- Sorry.

96
00:07:42.158 --> 00:07:44.078
Hit her green anbairn
claideblunanockt.

97
00:07:44.168 --> 00:07:47.498
I am a young.
beautiful woman.

98
00:07:47.538 --> 00:07:49.337
Concentrate. Willow.

99
00:07:49.418 --> 00:07:51.587
Hit her green anbairn
claideblunanockt.

100
00:07:51.668 --> 00:07:54.047
Hither greenan bairn
claideb lunanockt.

101
00:07:54.127 --> 00:07:56.257
No!
You're losing me!

102
00:07:56.347 --> 00:07:59.767
-Hit her green anbairn claideblunanockt.

103
00:08:02.727 --> 00:08:04.687
Hit her green anbairn
claideb-

104
00:08:04.727 --> 00:08:07.767
- Aah! Aah!
- You all right? Nice try. Willow.

105
00:08:15.817 --> 00:08:19.788
Farmers!
Cherlindrea sends me farmers!

106
00:08:19.868 --> 00:08:23.368
Whew! The Nelwyn
really butchered that one.

107
00:08:23.408 --> 00:08:25.368
- I'm sorry. Raziel.
- You want out?

108
00:08:25.368 --> 00:08:26.708
- I'm sorry. Raziel.
- You want out?

109
00:08:26.748 --> 00:08:29.708
Basy. We can pick a lock.
Come on.

110
00:08:29.748 --> 00:08:31.708
No. No. no.
Like this!

111
00:08:31.757 --> 00:08:33.717
I know what I'm doing.
It's my spear. Leave it alone.

112
00:08:33.757 --> 00:08:37.717
Let me do it.
Out of the way. rodents.

113
00:08:38.757 --> 00:08:40.557
Take your hand off that.

114
00:08:40.637 --> 00:08:45.097
You leave that alone.
you stupid. fat Daikini!

115
00:08:45.187 --> 00:08:46.807
Ow!

116
00:08:46.897 --> 00:08:48.977
Dust of broken hearts.

117
00:08:59.737 --> 00:09:02.578
Ha. ha!
You are free!

118
00:09:02.618 --> 00:09:06.918
Come on. Madmartigan.
Let's get Blora Danan out of here.

119
00:09:06.958 --> 00:09:11.087
- Yeah. It'll be fun.
- Come on!

120
00:09:22.757 --> 00:09:26.807
- Are you all right?
- Yeah.

121
00:09:26.887 --> 00:09:28.977
I feel... good.

122
00:09:29.057 --> 00:09:32.607
- The dust of broken hearts.
- Ah-

123
00:09:32.687 --> 00:09:35.237
Hey. come on!

124
00:09:40.698 --> 00:09:43.828
- Let me see!
- Let me see. You always see.

125
00:09:43.908 --> 00:09:46.328
There's Blora. right there.
on those furs.

126
00:09:48.748 --> 00:09:50.918
Hey. wait! Leave this to us.

127
00:09:50.998 --> 00:09:53.708
- It's too dangerous for you.
- Only one of us should go in there.

128
00:09:53.797 --> 00:09:56.627
I've got experience in this
sort of thing. I know what I'm doing.

129
00:10:23.908 --> 00:10:26.828
Uh-oh.

130
00:10:26.868 --> 00:10:30.828
Wait. Shh. No! No! Madm-

131
00:10:41.337 --> 00:10:44.177
- I love you.
- Madmartigan!

132
00:10:44.257 --> 00:10:47.217
- What are you doing?
- Take the baby and go! Come on!

133
00:10:47.307 --> 00:10:49.227
Come on!

134
00:10:59.317 --> 00:11:01.527
- Oh. Sorsha.
- Oh!

135
00:11:03.237 --> 00:11:06.237
Wake from
this hateful sleep.

136
00:11:06.328 --> 00:11:08.698
It deprives me
of your beauty.

137
00:11:08.788 --> 00:11:12.748
- The beauty of your eyes-
- One move. jackass.

138
00:11:12.828 --> 00:11:15.208
and you really
will be a woman.

139
00:11:16.587 --> 00:11:20.547
You are my sun!
My moon!

140
00:11:20.627 --> 00:11:25.097
My starlit sky.
Without you. I dwell in darkness.

141
00:11:25.177 --> 00:11:29.267
- I love you.
- What are you doing here?

142
00:11:29.347 --> 00:11:32.687
Your power has enchanted me.
I stand helpless against it.

143
00:11:32.727 --> 00:11:34.687
Come to me. now.

144
00:11:34.767 --> 00:11:37.227
Tonight. let me
worship you in my arms.

145
00:11:37.317 --> 00:11:40.027
- Get away from me!
- I love you!

146
00:11:40.107 --> 00:11:42.567
Stop saying that!

147
00:11:42.607 --> 00:11:46.908
How can I stop the beating of
my heart? It pounds like never before.

148
00:11:46.987 --> 00:11:49.538
- Out of fear.
- Out of love!

149
00:11:49.618 --> 00:11:52.118
I can stop it.
I'll kill you.

150
00:11:52.208 --> 00:11:55.127
Death. next to love.
is a trivial thing.

151
00:11:57.958 --> 00:12:00.418
Your touch is worth
100.000 deaths.

152
00:12:03.677 --> 00:12:05.217
- What goes on here?

153
00:12:05.217 --> 00:12:06.297
- What goes on here?

154
00:12:11.977 --> 00:12:13.977
Deceiver!

155
00:12:15.557 --> 00:12:17.437
Stop him!

156
00:12:26.368 --> 00:12:28.987
Captain. getup!

157
00:12:39.418 --> 00:12:44.087
- You are great.

158
00:12:44.168 --> 00:12:47.007
Get on that shield!

159
00:12:58.397 --> 00:13:00.977
Sorsha!

160
00:13:03.607 --> 00:13:05.647
After them!

161
00:13:12.368 --> 00:13:14.748
- Whoa! Hey!

162
00:13:19.538 --> 00:13:21.498
They're getting away!

163
00:13:30.347 --> 00:13:32.597
-Follow me. Rool. I don't know.
- Where are you?

164
00:13:32.677 --> 00:13:36.887
- Aah! Ooh.
- Oh. no. where did everybody go?

165
00:13:36.977 --> 00:13:38.897
Maybe it was
something we said.

166
00:14:32.948 --> 00:14:36.078
Ohh-h-h-h!

167
00:14:57.267 --> 00:14:59.267
Madmartigan!

168
00:15:16.078 --> 00:15:20.328
- Madmartigan!
- What the hell happened up there?

169
00:15:20.408 --> 00:15:22.828
You started spouting poetry.

170
00:15:22.868 --> 00:15:25.458
- Poetry?
- Yeah.

171
00:15:25.538 --> 00:15:28.797
"I love you. Sorsha.
I worship you. Sorsha."

172
00:15:28.877 --> 00:15:30.797
You almost got us killed!

173
00:15:30.877 --> 00:15:32.837
"I love you. Sorsha"?

174
00:15:32.877 --> 00:15:35.297
I don't love her.
She kicked me in the face.

175
00:15:35.387 --> 00:15:38.807
I hate her! Don't I?

176
00:15:40.977 --> 00:15:43.437
Kael! Kael!

177
00:15:43.477 --> 00:15:46.147
Nockmaar soldiers!

178
00:15:48.147 --> 00:15:51.607
Hoy! Get the children! Come on!

179
00:15:54.357 --> 00:15:56.328
- Get the children!
- They're after us! We need to hide.

180
00:15:56.368 --> 00:15:59.487
Come on. Follow me. Quick!
Come on! Move!

181
00:16:15.967 --> 00:16:17.717
I knew you'd
get out of that rattrap.

182
00:16:17.717 --> 00:16:18.677
I knew you'd
get out of that rattrap.

183
00:16:21.267 --> 00:16:23.227
You left me to die. Airk.

184
00:16:23.267 --> 00:16:24.477
I probably saved your life.

185
00:16:24.557 --> 00:16:26.557
We were slaughtered
and I lost a lot of good-

186
00:16:26.647 --> 00:16:28.977
- Shh! Quiet!

187
00:16:30.067 --> 00:16:32.027
Tear this village apart!

188
00:16:32.067 --> 00:16:36.487
Look everywhere!
Find the child!

189
00:16:45.368 --> 00:16:48.837
- Shh!

190
00:16:54.677 --> 00:16:56.587
Shh-shh-shh!

191
00:17:12.277 --> 00:17:15.317
Tell Sorsha
I search the north bank!

192
00:17:15.397 --> 00:17:17.317
- Hah! Hah!
- Yes. General.

193
00:17:30.458 --> 00:17:32.498
- Quiet. Shh!

194
00:17:51.897 --> 00:17:54.897
- Sorsha!
- Back.

195
00:17:54.987 --> 00:17:56.647
Back!

196
00:18:03.328 --> 00:18:05.908
Back!

197
00:18:05.998 --> 00:18:10.248
- Keep the baby quiet.
- She needs to be changed.

198
00:18:10.328 --> 00:18:12.127
- Nockmaar scum!
- You'll never defeat us.

199
00:18:12.168 --> 00:18:13.998
- Give up the baby!
- Shut up!

200
00:18:16.007 --> 00:18:17.668
What does Bavmorda want
with this baby. anyway?

201
00:18:17.757 --> 00:18:19.507
She's a princess.

202
00:18:19.587 --> 00:18:21.427
- We're taking her to Tir Asleen.
- Tir Asleen?

203
00:18:21.507 --> 00:18:24.427
Even if you could
find it. peck.

204
00:18:24.507 --> 00:18:26.847
she's right-you'd never
get past the Nockmaar army.

205
00:18:26.927 --> 00:18:29.387
There's an even bigger
army at Tir Asleen.

206
00:18:29.477 --> 00:18:31.977
- If we can just get there-

207
00:18:35.357 --> 00:18:38.147
I've lost more than half
my men fighting Bavmorda.

208
00:18:38.198 --> 00:18:40.817
Now you and this peck
are gonna take her on?

209
00:18:40.857 --> 00:18:44.158
You always told me you served
no one. Madmartigan.

210
00:18:44.198 --> 00:18:46.158
Since when are
you a crusader?

211
00:18:48.458 --> 00:18:51.708
He's not gonna help you. peck.

212
00:18:51.788 --> 00:18:53.788
He's a worthless thief.

213
00:18:55.208 --> 00:18:57.627
I'm not a thief. Airk.

214
00:18:57.708 --> 00:19:00.677
He's not a thief.

215
00:19:00.717 --> 00:19:02.967
Are you?

216
00:19:17.527 --> 00:19:21.357
I serve the Nelwyn. Airk.

217
00:19:26.078 --> 00:19:28.658
- Want to come with us?
- You'll never make it. Madmartigan.

218
00:19:30.578 --> 00:19:32.538
Then once again
we say good-bye.

219
00:19:46.347 --> 00:19:49.767
- Over here!
- Sorsha!

220
00:19:49.847 --> 00:19:53.227
Weapons down or she's dead!

221
00:19:58.437 --> 00:20:00.147
Hyah! Hyah!

222
00:20:05.777 --> 00:20:08.698
- Hyah!
- Get to your horses! After 'em!

223
00:20:54.868 --> 00:20:57.418
This way!
This way!

224
00:20:57.498 --> 00:21:00.168
As the crow flies. you fools!

225
00:21:07.047 --> 00:21:09.927
- You're holding me too tight!
- I don't want you to get away.

226
00:21:10.007 --> 00:21:14.847
Why? Because I'm your sun.
your moon. your starlit sky?

227
00:21:16.397 --> 00:21:18.647
Get your hair out of my face.
or I'll chop it off.

228
00:21:22.477 --> 00:21:26.448
Did I really- Did I really
say those things last night?

229
00:21:26.527 --> 00:21:29.658
- In your tent?
- You said you loved me.

230
00:21:29.698 --> 00:21:32.198
- I don't remember that.
- You lied to me!

231
00:21:32.288 --> 00:21:34.658
No. I-

232
00:21:34.748 --> 00:21:37.208
I just wasn't myself
last night.

233
00:21:37.248 --> 00:21:41.627
I suppose my power enchanted you.
and you were helpless against it.

234
00:21:41.708 --> 00:21:44.668
- Um. sort of.
- Then what?

235
00:21:44.717 --> 00:21:46.837
It went away.

236
00:21:46.877 --> 00:21:50.547
It went away?
"I dwell in darkness without you."

237
00:21:50.637 --> 00:21:52.717
- and it went away?
- Yeah.

238
00:22:03.857 --> 00:22:07.948
- Whoa.

239
00:22:14.748 --> 00:22:17.208
Hurry! Kael's coming!

240
00:22:21.748 --> 00:22:24.047
Madmartigan. come on!
Now!

241
00:22:32.047 --> 00:22:35.637
Madmartigan. come on!

242
00:22:35.717 --> 00:22:38.517
They're coming! Away!

243
00:22:38.597 --> 00:22:40.847
Go on! Hyah!

244
00:22:57.868 --> 00:23:00.998
Whoa! Whoa!

245
00:23:01.078 --> 00:23:03.248
This way!

246
00:23:08.797 --> 00:23:12.587
Tir Asleen! At last. Tir Asleen!

247
00:23:23.477 --> 00:23:25.437
Hello?

